data.description: Peace and Privacy!  This Crystal Creek home is nestled nicely with a oversized lot and large, mature trees!  Overlook your large backyard w/ no backyard neighbors from the 2-tier deck!  This 4 bedroom home comes w/ a large private suite accompanied by a walk-in closet!  2 total bedrooms and bathrooms upstairs, along with a large kitchen, dining area, & living room!  Head downstairs to the family room w/ gas fireplace, 2 additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, laundry, and basement garage access!  The gas heated garage w/ floor drain will keep you active in the winter, and plenty of room for storage or hobbies!
